Company Description: Established IN 1948, Mcdonald's Corporation Is A Fast Food Company. Based IN Green Brook, N.J., It Is A Global Foodservice Retailer Operating One Of The Largest Chains Of Franchised Outlets (Mcdonald's). Its Menu Consists Of Various Items, Including Burgers, Sandwiches, Salads, Snacks And Sides, Beverages, Desserts And Shakes. It Also Offers Some Of Its Flagship Products, Including Big Mac Sandwich, Quarter Pounder, Chicken Mcnuggets, Egg Mcmuffin And Mcgourmet Dinners. Mcdonald's Provides Both Fruit And Vegetable Option For Its Trademark Happy Meals, Such As Fruit Bags, Corn Cups And Apple Dippers. The Company Also Offers Entertainment Options Such As Free WI-Fi, Arch Card/Play Places And Party Services. For Over 20 Years, Mcdonald's Partners The Environmental Defense Fund.
